{"tid":275600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（年經）肥婆真係好撚黑人憎","createTime":"2017-06-08T07:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T16:55:53.000Z","uid":58318,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e255a6bd759ac51d050fb07578614ec5f547fa","tid":275600,"uid":58318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:01:41.000Z","msg":"你地講得岩肥婆真係好撚黑人憎<br />\n本以為識左個好既肥婆<br />\n點知都係天下烏鴉一樣黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日以為自己著衫好撚靚<br />\n又唔知自己啲肉嗶晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔知佢哪來的自信著一字膊出街<br />\n又冇鎖骨 又冇頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲肥婆摺入面啲老泥成尺厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日又話自己要減肥<br />\n食野又食鬼死咁多<br />\n話借少少黎食 屌你老母 同我食撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母死肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f233c245646c2c26c257743a284cb28b38479b3","tid":275600,"uid":58318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9acc7aa458e0ba95c3bda585011844157be6a2","tid":275600,"uid":101717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:53:16.000Z","msg":"肥婆真係好撚自信 成撚日笑尻啲瘦過自己既人肥 又講撚到自己減肥專家咁 都唔望下自己個油淋淋大肚腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150bbc09c6e72ab6286f3d161e43c27e36e48d6c","tid":275600,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci